{
  "stem": "17606.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 184.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], who was-- Wacek, who was in charge of the execution, managed to get very close to his car, and put two bullets in him and killed him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But also, he paid with his life for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And, of course, the entire area was surrounded immediately by Gestapo and SS men, and I was arrested.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I only had in my pocket two hand grenades and two guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They didn't arrest me as a participant, only as a-- I don't know, why-- maybe-- maybe I'm involved with-- hundreds of Poles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Put me in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] but 30 or 40 and pushed into this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I dispose in the wagon of the guns and of the grenades.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Although, it didn't mean anything, if they'll discover-- if they'll take-- they'll get me into the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "If I have the grenades or not, I'll be shot, because the first thing they said, pull down your pants.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Excuse my expressions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But anyhow, I had a habit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I always had in my pocket a swastika.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "For two purposes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "First of all, I felt much more comfortable riding with the German in the front of the platform, the front platform, then with the Poles who could recognize me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "After all, I was raised in War-- in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "All day, they could feel out a Jew through three pair of underwear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "With them, I mean, a Volksdeutsche who doesn't speak German, it was normal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But they called them [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They called the Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And felt-- so I had that swastika in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "So once they put us in a room for interrogation, I started to canvas the ro-- the room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I opened one door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "It's a broom closet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I open another door, it was some other garbage there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
